OL,7,FA dad who had an obsession with gore
OL,8,Fand gruesome horror has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor life after he murdered then
OL,10,Fdismembered his housemate in "an
OL,11,Falmost unbelievably cold-blooded and
OL,12,Fmacabre way".
OL,14,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, who also has
OL,15,Fa tattoo of slasher-film character
OL,16,FJason from Friday The 13th, bludgeoned
OL,17,FStuart Everett with a hammer at the
OL,18,Fhouse they shared in Winton, Salford.
