OL,5,Cman
OL,7,FHe then used a hacksaw to dismember
OL,8,Fhis 67-year-old housemate and friend
OL,9,Fbefore taking the body parts in
OL,10,Fplastic bags on bus journeys across
OL,11,FSalford and north Manchester to dump
OL,12,Fthe evidence.
OL,14,FThe Polish national later pretended to
OL,15,Fbe Mr Everett to throw friends and
OL,16,Ffamily off the trail, using his phone
OL,17,Fand bank cards, as well as sending a
OL,18,Fbirthday card in his name to his
OL,19,Fbrother, after his death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
