OL,7,FMajerkiewicz, a dad-of-two with his
OL,8,FPolish ex-partner, denied
OL,9,Fresponsibility for the killing but
OL,10,Foffered no evidence in his defence and
OL,11,Fhis motive remains unclear.
OL,13,FJurors convicted him of murder in
OL,14,Funder two hours of deliberations
OL,15,Ffollowing a three-week trial at
OL,16,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,18,FJailing him for a minimum of 34 years
OL,19,Fyears Mr Justice Cavanagh told
OL,20,FMajerkiewicz, who looked ahead with no
OL,21,Femotion, he had shown no remorse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
