OL,7,FHe said: "You acted in an almost
OL,8,Funbelievably cold-blooded and macabre
OL,9,Fway, and showed complete disrespect
OL,10,Fand contempt for your friend's remains.
OL,12,F"This denied dignity to Stuart Everett
OL,13,Feven in death, and greatly increased
OL,14,Fthe pain suffered by Stuart Everett's
OL,15,Ffamily when the murder came to light."
OL,17,FHe added: "Through the way in which
OL,18,Fyou behaved in the aftermath of Stuart
OL,19,FEverett's death showed an extremely
OL,20,Fdistasteful willingness and perhaps
OL,21,Feven enthusiasm to butcher his body."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
