OL,7,FManchester Crown Court previously
OL,8,Fheard that Mr Everett was murdered
OL,9,Fovernight between 27 and 28 March 2024.
OL,11,FThe former civil servant's fate was
OL,12,Fonly revealed when a member of the
OL,13,Fpublic found Mr Everett's lower torso
OL,14,Fand thighs, wrapped in cling film, in
OL,15,Fan abandoned bunker in Kersal Dale
OL,16,Fnature reserve, in Salford, in April
OL,17,F2024.
