OL,8,Fother locations across Salford and
OL,9,Fnorth Manchester in the weeks
OL,10,Ffollowing, but only a third of his
OL,11,Fbody has ever been recovered.
OL,13,FPolice scoured CCTV from the area and
OL,14,Fdiscovered, two days before, a man
OL,15,Fentering the wooded area carrying a
OL,16,Fheavy blue bag before emerging shortly
OL,17,Fafter without it.
