OL,7,FHis identity was unknown but three
OL,8,Fweeks later Majerkiewicz was spotted
OL,9,Fby an officer working on the case who
OL,10,Fdrove past him by chance and noted he
OL,11,Flooked like the man from the CCTV.
OL,13,FThe suspect told officers they had
OL,14,Fmade a "mistake 100%" as he was
OL,15,Farrested.
OL,17,FWhen police searched his address in
OL,18,FWinton, Salford, they found evidence
OL,19,Fof blood on a carpet and furniture and
OL,20,Fan attempted clean-up after the
OL,21,Fkilling and dismemberment.
