OL,7,FIn 2013 he began living in a three-bed
OL,8,Fterrace house on Worsley Road in the
OL,9,FWinton area of Salford and began sub-
OL,10,Fletting the two other bedrooms, with
OL,11,FMajerkiewicz, moving in during 2017.
OL,13,FThe defendant had worked as a manager
OL,14,Fat fast-food shops in the Trafford
OL,15,FCentre but was unemployed at the time
OL,16,Fof the murder, with financial
OL,17,Fpressures building in the household
OL,18,Fand Majerkiewicz around #60,000 in
OL,19,Fdebt.
