OL,7,FAfter the initial torso discovery,
OL,8,Fpolice launched Operation Harker,
OL,9,Ffinding evidence in 15 crime scenes
OL,10,Fand human remains at five different
OL,11,Fsites.
OL,13,FDetectives pieced together thousands
OL,14,Fof hours of CCTV, tracking the
OL,15,Fdefendant's movements, also
OL,16,Fdiscovering human remains at Linnyshaw
OL,17,FColliery Woods, Blackleach Reservoir,
OL,18,FWorsley Woods and Boggart Hole Clough.
